  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But everybody wanted to work like that because there was always a chance to get something to eat somewhere from the field, especially corn.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had what they call in Czech [CZECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CZECH] is corn, the corn fields and et cetera.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We had a Jewish girl who took care of us [? outside ?] and some man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the SS was around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you make a go of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't, not there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I had certain experiences there because the one who took care of us out there had a way of telling [? us. ?] We were in a field right near the [?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ohre, ?] which a river in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were like big green bushes there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then when she saw that, some of the girls got very tired or so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said, oh, lay down and sleep for a little while, or rest for a little while.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my one experience was there that near Theresienstadt was what they called the [GERMAN], the small-- it was clearly the concentration camp, not the ghetto, and-- which was very bad, which we didn't even know how bad it was at that time already.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ok.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
